"The opening of the 2021 China International Rail Transportation and Equipment Manufacturing Talent Summit - Rolling News - Hunan Daily Online - Huasheng Online"
"Hunan Daily December 10th news (Full media reporter Zhou Shiheng) On the 9th, the 2021 China International Rail Transportation and Equipment Manufacturing Talent Summit, known as "Zhi Hui Xiao Xiang", opened in Zhuzhou."
"Provincial Party Standing Committee and Minister of the Provincial Party Organization Department Wang Cheng attended the launch ceremony and delivered a speech."
"Wang Cheng pointed out that holding a talent summit is an important measure to implement the spirit of the central talent work conference and the 12th provincial party congress, demonstrating Hunan's sincere sincerity in valuing, thirsting for, and making good use of talent."
"Hunan has a fine tradition of valuing, loving, and respecting talent, a broad platform to help talent development, and favorable conditions for a better life. In recent years, it has deeply implemented the talent-led development strategy, taking the Lotus Talent Action Plan as the guide, and has established a full-chain talent work pattern to cultivate, retain, and use talent, becoming a fertile soil for talent growth and achievement, a hotbed for innovation and entrepreneurship, and a joyful place to live and work."
"Currently, Hunan is comprehensively implementing its "three highs and four news" strategic positioning and mission, further opening the door to talent and merit, providing better policies for talent innovation and entrepreneurship, focusing more resources, and creating better conditions. It is expected that outstanding talents from all sectors will gather wisdom and strength to contribute to Hunan's high-quality development."
At the event, there were exhibits set up for Changsha, Zhuzhou, Xiangtan and Hunan Free Trade Zone. The Provincial Department of Science and Technology, the Provincial Department of Industry and Information Technology, and the Provincial Department of Human Resources and Social Security released lists of key requirements for technological innovation in advanced manufacturing industries, catalogs of talent needs in the intelligent manufacturing industry, and catalogs of young talent needs in the intelligent manufacturing industry for postdoctoral mobile stations.
During the event, 48 large enterprises such as CRRC, Zhonglian Heavy Industry, and Far East Technology were on-site to recruit talent, and nearly a thousand recent graduates and social talents participated in the talent project docking.